@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Downloads";
}

<section class="page-shell">
    <span class="eyebrow">Downloads</span>
    <h1>Artefatos publicos do DDS StudyOS</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        Esta pagina existe para centralizar os links oficiais do app. O canal publico continua no
        repositório de updates, e o portal apenas organiza o acesso.
    </p>

    <div class="info-grid">
        <article class="panel">
            <h2>Canal estavel</h2>
            <p>Instalador completo para uso geral.</p>
            <a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates/releases/latest/download/DDSStudyOS-Setup.exe">
                Baixar DDSStudyOS-Setup.exe
            </a>
        </article>

        <article class="panel">
            <h2>Canal beta</h2>
            <p>Build para validacao incremental em campo.</p>
            <a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates/releases/latest/download/DDSStudyOS-Beta-Setup.exe">
                Baixar DDSStudyOS-Beta-Setup.exe
            </a>
        </article>

        <article class="panel">
            <h2>Portable</h2>
            <p>Pacote compacto para testes sem instalacao tradicional.</p>
            <a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates/releases/latest/download/DDSStudyOS-Portable.zip">
                Baixar DDSStudyOS-Portable.zip
            </a>
        </article>
    </div>

    <div class="secondary-panel">
        <strong>Repositorio oficial de distribuicao</strong>
        <p>
            Todos os arquivos publicos e manifests continuam publicados no GitHub:
            <a href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates/releases">DDSStudyOS-Updates/releases</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

    <a class="back-link" href="/">Voltar para a home publica</a>
</section>

<style>
    .page-shell {
        max-width: 1040px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 36px 24px 48px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #7c5cff;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #eef2ff;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
    }
    .lead, .panel p, .secondary-panel p {
        color: #c9d4ea;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .info-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 28px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    }
    .panel, .secondary-panel {
        border: 1px solid rgba(164, 180, 215, 0.16);
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: rgba(8, 14, 30, 0.84);
        padding: 22px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }
    .panel h2, .secondary-panel strong {
        display: block;
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: #f6f8ff;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
    }
    .primary-link, .secondary-panel a, .back-link {
        color: #8ea6ff;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .secondary-panel {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .back-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin-top: 24px;
    }
</style>
